text: Lovely 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom country cottage directly across the street from the Skagit River and nestled amongst mature trees. Comfortable open kitchen/living area with large windows. Spacious wrap-around deck with river views. Newer roof 2 years ago on house and garage. Sold with furniture. House was raised above the flood plain several years ago.

With a bright and modern aesthetic, you'll find everything you've been looking for in this Skagit Highlands Home. Intentional updates throughout include fresh paint, laminate & tile flooring & updated lighting. You'll love the privacy offered by the fully fenced-in backyard, which includes room for your pup and patio space for grilling and entertaining. The primary suite features a large bedroom, soaking tub, stall shower, roomy vanity, and expansive walk-in closet. The oversized landing makes for a great work-from-home space, TV nook, or flex space. With an attached two-car garage & driveway parking, you'll have space for everything. All appliances are included, making this an easy transition to home . Check out the nearby park & trails!

Escape to paradise at this exquisite Lake Cavanaugh waterfront retreat! Spanning 3, 000 square feet, this home offers a seamless blend of luxury and comfort, showcasing stunning lake views from every angle. Entertain with ease in the spacious, open-concept living areas, where large windows flood the space with natural light and frame picturesque scenes of the serene waters. Step outside to the expansive deck and envision hosting the ultimate Fourth of July celebration. Boating enthusiasts will delight in the convenience of the hydraulic boat lift. Whether you're fishing, water skiing, or simply cruising along the shoreline, this property offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment.

Dramatic panoramic views of the Guemes Channel from this desirable building lot perched above the water. Imagine expansive windows of your new contemporary dream home watching boats gracefully travel the channel framed by the Cascade mountains with views all the way to Canada. The perfect backdrop to build your relaxing PNW haven. Enjoy painted sunset views over the San Juan Islands. A blank canvas of limitless possibilities awaiting creativity and imagination. Architectural drawings help show what transformation may be possible, bringing your design to reality.

Newly updated house in Bow Situated in a community surrounded by farmland, a variety of restaurants & world class recreation activities. Located 4 minutes from I-5 is ideal for commuters that enjoy a rural atmosphere. The roof top deck off the primary bedroom is ideal for viewing sunsets over the San Juans and endless stargazing. Enjoy gardening in the rich Samish soil without the expense of flood insurance. The property features a custom craftsman style house and a historic workshop ready to be converted into an ADU, home business or hobby studio. Don't miss your opportunity to put down roots in this highly sought after area.

Spacious 1848 sf rambler featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Primary bedroom with ensuite and doors accessing the back yard. The kitchen is open to dining area, living room and has french doors that access the large bonus room with vaulted ceilings. Bonus room is filled with lots of light due to the french doors on the north and sound end of the room. Very private yard with mature plants, fruit trees and brand-new landscaping in progress. Storage shed in back yard is perfect for all your yard and hobby extras. This home is located in a prime location close to Parks, Playgrounds, Walking trail along Skagit River, Schools, Shopping and more!

Beautiful restored classic! Enjoy the charm & detail of this classic with the comforts of modern living. Original hardwood floors, high ceilings, gorgeous trim boards, cozy fireplace, walk in pantry and clawfoot tub are just some of the amazing touches this light and bright home includes. Outside the private fully fenced back yard with new deck and built in gazebo is perfect for entertaining. Close to downtown Mount Vernon which offers a vibrant mix of restaurants, galleries and shops. Or take a stroll on the riverwalk along the gorgeous Skagit River. You will enjoy all the richness of Skagit County amidst the picturesque surroundings of mountains, farmland and waterways with this beautiful turn of the century home!

Plans and permits for Townhomes on Waugh Road; four-plex & triplex for a total of seven units on a single parcel. All utilities (sewer, PUD water, Cascade natural gas, PSE, Comcast, Verizon telephone), are to the site. Curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and curb cuts per City specifications, plus mailbox kiosk and off-site storm retention pond provided to the north according to City requirements. Nice territorial and mountain views from a level lot!

Discover the perfect blend of convenience and charm in Anacortes! This stunning rambler-style duplex, offering a total of 2110 sqft, is an ideal investment for both first-time homebuyers and seasoned investors. Nestled just minutes from downtown Anacortes, Burrows Pass, Washington Park, Skyline Marina, and an array of parks, this property combines serene living with easy access to local attractions. Each unit features 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and an attached private garage, promising comfort and privacy. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of Anacortes' tranquility and convenience. Explore the potential today!

Adorable single story, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a great layout. Fresh paint and new roof! Fully fenced yard with lawn and room for a garden! Enclosed entry porch with utility room and pantry. Detached 468 sq ft shop/garage with excellent storage and covered work space. Asphalt driveway and gated entry. Walking distance to downtown Burlington with fantastic dining and shopping and just moments to I5.

Discover tranquility on Bacus Hill with this charming 20-acre property! Enjoy a meticulously maintained custom rambler featuring 3 bedrooms, 2+ baths, and 1822 sq/ft of living space. Cozy up by the wood stove in the living room or relax in the family room by the gas fireplace. Heat pump provides efficient heating or cooling. The updated kitchen boasts granite countertops. Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom with a luxurious full bath and walk-in closet. Outside, enjoy landscaped gardens, a fenced garden area, and a firepit. Plus, a 1700+ sq/ft shop with a wood stove and half bath, and a separate machine shed/woodshed offering additional storage. Home and shop even have a brand new roof! This home is the one you've been waiting for!

This beautifully maintained rambler is located in a sought-after neighborhood close to downtown Burlington. Inside, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms, one is a primary suite with an updated 3/4 bathroom. A well-lit formal living room, family room, and dining room open to gourmet kitchen overlooking your beautifully landscaped fully fenced back and side yard. Attached is a fully enclosed Sunroom and large entertainment deck, detached storage building w/power, 2-car garage with storage and cabinets. So much more to list, stop by and see. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home in an excellent location, off Hwy 20, for convenient access to shopping and I-5.

A beautiful Craftsman Bungalow right in town awaits! Gorgeous features showcasing its period with statement crown moldings, wainscoting, solid wood doors, age specific finishes & fir floors throughout. The main floor has a spacious feel creating great flow between entry and formal living and dining with the help of the high ceilings. Quintessential kitchen with garden window and eating nook and a primary on the main and full bath. Second level has 4 bedrooms with walk-in closets! Lower-level basement is roughed in and ready for you to make it yours with the makings of two rooms started. Great location on a corner lot with 2 car detached garage and parking off of the alley all within minutes to downtown shops and eateries. Welcome home!

Beautiful rambler in the River's Edge neighborhood! This Four Bedroom, 1.75 Bath is everything you have been looking for! Open concept Family Room, Kitchen & eating area provides plenty of space for entertaining your friends and loved ones. The cook will love the Kitchen area with the stainless appliances, gas cooktop, pull out drawers for easy storage & an island big enough for a crowd. Cozy backyard fully fenced for your privacy and minimal maintenance. Three car garage provides plenty of space to park and still have room for a shop or home gym. A/C too! A short walk from the local boat launch & just minutes away from parks, restaurants & Burlington shopping.

Custom-built 1800 sqft , 3bed/2bath home with unparalleled privacy, craftsmanship, and meticulous maintenance nestled on serene acreage. For peace of mind, a security system is installed; power continuity is assured with a whole-house generator. Remain comfortable through all seasons with your heat pump, propane furnace, wood stove, and a sealed crawlspace to enhance energy efficiency. Property features a shop with ample space for hobbies and projects. Other outbuildings offer generous storage options as well as dedicated RV storage. Outdoors, this haven has fruit trees and expansive garden space. To enhance your enjoyment, there is a large deck, firepit, and hot tub. Dont miss this opportunity to make this sanctuary your home!

2.5 Acre Residential Homesite. Located on Buchanan Hill above Clear Lake. West-facing lot has a gentle slope allowing for a wide variety of house designs. Plenty of room for a shop as well as animals, gardens and recreation. Private setting, with a mix of treed and grassy areas, the access is off an established driveway that leads to a choice of home sites. PUD water is at the street, PSE power transformer on the lot so underground power will be available to your new residence. This type of property rarely becomes available. This newly developed lot may be the answer to your searches. The location is just minutes from I-5 and Mount Vernon, yet the surrounding area is very rural and dotted with other fine homes. Make it yours!

Don't miss this opportunity! Imagine owning a 5-acre property in desirable Bow with stunning views of the Skagit Valley, Bay, & Islands! This property features a 3-bedroom rambler & a large shop/2-car garage. Set back from Colony Road, down a driveway lined with mature cedar trees, sits a 1995 time capsule. The house remains in its original condition, including the kitchen, bathrooms, carpets & exterior deck. Update the home as much or as little as you desire! The serene property gently slopes towards the view, showcasing magnificent original landscaping with blooming rhododendrons, fruit trees, & more. The unfinished basement, with exterior access, offers an opportunity to add square footage or create a rental suite/ AirBnB.

This single story home blends modern luxury with classic charm featuring all the contemporary amenities you desire in a new home. The open-concept layout with plenty of natural light enhances the spacious feel, creating a perfect setting for both comfortable living & entertaining. The kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, granite countertops & storage. The allure doesn't end indoors step outside into your private oasis. The professionally landscaped yard is a masterpiece, showcasing a manicured lawn, and an array of textures plus a covered deck. A brand-new swim spa that beckons you to indulge in relaxation and fitness year-round. This high-end addition elevates your outdoor living offering a perfect blend of luxury and wellness.

Experience comfortable living, stunning three-bedroom, 2332sqft home w/large 3 car garage in desirable Cambridge Commons. Open & spacious kitchen w/central island and dining area, enjoy evenings by the gas fireplace in living room. Retreat to the main level primary bedroom w/bathroom & walk-in closet. Need a quiet space to work or relax? Look no further - The den/office provides the perfect solution, along with a separate laundry room for added functionality. Upstairs, discover two good sized bedrooms, a full bath, and a bonus room, providing ample space for relaxation and recreation. Fully fenced backyard, complete w/covered patio, perfect for entertaining. Community includes a fenced dog park and neighborhood park with playground.

Gorgeous remodeled home w ocean and island views. Fully remodeled light-filled main level w plank flooring features an open floor plan w high ceiling, wood beam accents, & plenty of windows & skylights. Entertain & enjoy the views from the spacious dining rm & living rm w floor to ceiling stone fireplace surround. Primary bedroom features heated floors & stunning bath w dual vanity & large walk-in glass & tile shower. Downstairs is an equally spacious living area w a second kitchen ready for your personal touch. Laundry/mud room w folding counter & plenty of storage. Outside enjoy views from the deck as well as pear, cherry, & apple trees, garden space, fire pit & plenty of parking space. Mini split for heat & A/C plus generator.

Entertain and enjoy mountain views from this spacious, window-filled Skagit Highlands home. The beautiful formal living room welcomes you with a cozy gas fireplace and plenty of room for friends. Open kitchen with bamboo floors, walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, and eating bar flows into the inviting dining room that provides plenty of room to gather and mingle. Upstairs enjoy the large, light-filled family room, primary bedroom with spacious bathroom that includes a soaking tub, large tile surround shower, and walk-in closet, plus good sized second and third bedrooms. Outside, enjoy the covered front porch, low maintenance yard, landscaping, and cozy patio.

This charming home, originally built in 1920, has been beautifully remodeled, blending vintage charm w/modern amenities. Step inside to discover the warmth of the original fir floors, reminding you of the home's heritage. Main house features 3 bedrooms & 1 bathroom, offering comfortable living spaces that are both inviting & functional. Modern appliances & stylish finishes, this kitchen is sure to impress. Outside, you'll find a delightful surprise - a tiny house ADU in the BY. This studio-style ADU provides a versatile space that can be used as a guest suite or rental opportunity. Windows & roof were replaced during the full remodel 6 years ago. Don't miss the opportunity to own this unique blend of historic charm & modern convenience.

Wonderful manufactured home in the popular Carriage Estates senior park! This well kept 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home features an open floor plan with vaulted ceiling. You'll love the spacious Primary bedroom, with full bathroom & walk-in closet! Nice private back yard with covered deck and 2 garden/storage sheds for your hobbies and garden tools! All this and is covered by a new roof and cooled with central heating and air conditioning! Come take a look at your NextHome!

Don't miss this spacious triple-wide on 11.47 acres. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, open floor plan with large kitchen, eating bar, tons of cabinets, pantry. Lots of natural light throughout home, double french doors opens to covered patio. Double doors open to huge primary bedroom with walk in closet and large primary bathroom with double vanity, shower and soaking tub.. Additional storage/mud room with seperate entrance off of laundry rm. Seller says B.E.H.S. or S.W.H.S.

Plans and permit for a four-plex townhome on Waugh Road. All utilities (sewer, PUD water, Cascade natural gas, PSE, Comcast, Verizon telephone), are to the site. Curbs, gutters, sidewalks, and curb cuts per City specifications, plus mailbox kiosk and off-site storm retention pond provided to the north according to City requirements. Nice territorial and mountain views from a level lot!

Enjoy country living just minutes from town. This 1966 Tri-Level home checks all the boxes. Just shy of an acre, quiet backyard with plenty of room for outdoor entertainment. Close to town but feels miles away. Come see for yourself all of the possibilities.

Looking for a cute updated bungalow in Sedro Woolley? Downsizing or ready for your starter home? Check out this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home on a corner lot with fully fenced yard. Gardner? The yard is an open slate ready for your landscaping design to bring it alive. There is some mature trees in front and along the side for a buffer from the street. The rear deck overlooks the backyard and is a perfect spot for entertaining or relaxing. The home just had the interior painted, new laminate flooring, new hot water tank and ready for you to move in! Plus, there is room in the back yard to put a shed or maybe build a small garage? Great opportunity to make this home your own!!

Welcome to Hilltop Haven in Mount Vernon! This stunning residence boasts thoughtful design and captivating features. Nestled amidst picturesque surroundings, it offers a tranquil retreat with impeccable landscaping. Inside, hardwood floors flow seamlessly, and three bedrooms ensure relaxation. Convenience is prioritized with two full and two half bathrooms. Den, bonus room, spacious utility room, three car garage, rec room, workshop and lots of storage space throughout. Host memorable events on the large deck. The daylight basement offers endless possibilities. Experience comfort and luxuryschedule your showing today!

Indulge in the allure of this captivating residence boasting breathtaking vistas of Mt. Baker and Padilla Bay. Immerse yourself in elegance with 10' ceilings, adorned with architectural cove crown molding and baseboards. Revel in the opulence of oak, travertine, and heated slate flooring, while double-sided fireplaces add warmth and charm. Work or unwind in the dedicated office, offering French doors leading to a charming courtyard. Retreat to the primary bedroom, featuring a luxurious ensuite with a soaking tub and walk-in shower. Delight in outdoor living with courtyards, decks, and patios, all within reach of the trailhead to Cranberry Lake. Experience luxury living at its finest in this remarkable abode. Washers & dryers on both levels

Welcome to your spacious retreat! This charming rambler offers over 2000 sq ft of modern living space on over 1/3 acre, backing onto a serene green belt. Freshly painted interiors and a new roof greet you inside. Enjoy seamless entertaining in the well-appointed kitchen and relax in the tranquil master suite with its attached spa-like bathroom. Additional upgrades include a new AC heat pump for year-round comfort. Outside, the expansive yard is perfect for outdoor activities and includes a hot tub for everyday relaxation. Conveniently located near amenities, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this modern living experience!

Unlock the door to your dream home with this expansive 1.4-acre property, offering the ideal canvas for your architectural aspirations. Nestled in a tranquil setting, graced by a picturesque seasonal creek and lush with timber, this plot ensures privacy and natural beauty. Water access is conveniently available through a cistern system or can be sourced from Fruitdale Rd, a mere 500 feet away. Power readily established on-site. Experience the liberty of expansive space - clear the land to suit your vision while preserving the natural environment. Enjoy the freedom of no HOA constraints and let your creativity reign supreme. Your perfect home awaits!

3 bedroom home with detached garage and DADU. Main house has a spacious kitchen with plenty of room to work. Cozy living room, den and formal dining area. Large lot, plenty of room for parking and still room for your RV and boat. Low maintenance back yard offers it ALL! Garden space, patio with pergola, swimming pool, playset, firepit and dog area too! Large, detached garage with plenty of space for parking or hobbies. Located close to Hwy 20 makes commuting easy, and convenient to downtown shopping and restaurants. Come check it out!

This newly remodeled 3 bedroom, .75 bath home offers modern comfort at an affordable price. All new kitchen, appliances, windows, and flooring. Easy highway access and conveniently located near stores. With updated interiors, new appliances, and a convenient location, it's the perfect blend of style and affordability. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to call this home yours!

Practically brand new haven nestled in the Shelter Bay community! This home boasts an inviting open-concept layout with vaulted ceilings and expansive windows bathing the space in natural light with large slider to backyard deck. Plus easy-to-maintain vinyl plank flooring. Enjoy cozy evenings by the chic electric fireplace, and entertain effortlessly in the fresh white kitchen featuring a walk-in pantry, quartz counters & spacious eat-at island. Retreat to the primary bedroom with its adjoining 3/4 bath featuring a floor-to-ceiling tile shower and walk-in closet. Another bedroom and full bath offer flexibility and convenience. With a 2-car garage and a charming yard awaiting your landscaping touch, this home is ready to fulfill your dreams.

Welcome home to this tidy, well maintained one level home boasting 4 bedrooms. Upon arrival you'll be taken in by the fantastic curb appeal and a warm, inviting atmosphere. It offers an efficient kitchen, living room with cozy gas fireplace, and lovely dining area which looks out at the spacious fenced back yard. Plant a garden, enjoy hosting summer gatherings or just relax on the patio. Outdoor adventures are beckoning you to explore the community forest land trails, just 2 blocks away, leading to nearby Little Cranberry Lake. Close to parks and schools. Single car garage plus RV parking. This home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience and tranquility. Easy commute to NAS Whidbey. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own!

Darling 2 BR, 1 Bath home w/ 1033 sq ft in downtown Sedro Woolley on a shy 1/4 acre corner lot. Yard is fully fenced. Newer vinyl windows, newer carpet in living room (original hardwood floors under carpeting). Cute built-in corner shelving units in dining room. Plaster walls, tile floors & tub surround in bath. Ductless HP Mini-split units in living & bedroom for heat as well as air conditioning in the summer. Detached 3 bay garage w/ shop area plus large 1 car carport. Room for garden, RV parking, nice gathering place in backyard, even a chicken coop! Close to downtown, schools & shopping. Possible potential to subdivide & get additional lot. Buyer to verify.

Nestled on a beautiful .86-acre lot on Guemes Island, this property is a nature lover's dream. Partially developed using eco-friendly methods, to ensure harmony with its natural surroundings, and accommodate a modern home site. Meticulous site preparation sets this lot apart. A survey has been completed, corners are flagged, lot certification and critical areas review are in hand. Soil logs have been recorded, water and power are available. Extensive tree work has been done to let in the light and clear around likely home, septic and garage sites. The driveway is base-graded and chipped, and this 3-lot property is landscaped with natural materials. Whether you envision a cozy cabin or a grand estate, this lot offers endless possibilities.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Single-story 3 bedroom home conveniently located in the heart of Mount Vernon. Step inside to discover beautiful wood flooring in the living area along with built in shelves and fireplace. This open-concept layout allows lots of natural light into the dining area and the kitchen. Entertain on the inviting deck. The partially fenced yard provides privacy while still allowing ample space for outdoor activities, surrounded by beautiful landscaping. Single car garage provides parking and storage along with extra gravel parking on the side. Easy access to I5, schools, parks, hospital and amenities.

Welcome home to this charming gem in the heart of Sedro-Woolley! Completely renovated from the studs out in 2020, this delightful house has modern upgrades & stylish finishes throughout. Step inside to discover ductless heat pumps providing efficient heating & cooling, for year-round comfort. The laminate floors add a touch of elegance, complementing the new roof, windows, and woodwork. Enjoy the convenience of an added half bath, ideal for guests and everyday use. The new kitchen features sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and quality appliances. Situated on a large lot, there's ample space for gardening enthusiasts or the opportunity to add a garage or workshop. This turnkey property is ready to welcome you home.
